@30141=~Attack Bonus - Moment of Prescience

Using this ability causes the character to gain a +25 attack bonus for 1 round. Only one of the three Moment of Prescience abilities can be used.

This ability may be used as a free action.~
@30142=~Armor Class Bonus - Moment of Prescience~
