Boulder Roll creates a large boulder, which rolls forward from the caster, crushing creatures in its path, until it hits a wall. Creatures hit take 12d8 bludgeoning damage and are knocked down for 2 rounds. A successful Reflex save halves the damage and prevents one from being knocked down. The boulder always travels due south from the caster.~
