Saving Throw: Fortitude half

By casting this spell, the caster emits a Void Sound, a horrific sound that can somehow be heard by the deaf and by no one else, and which carries negative energy with it. All deaf creatures in the area of effect take 1d8 magic damage per level (max 30d8). This spell has no effect on undead or constructs.~
