Duration: 8 hours or until all charges are expended
Casting Time: 10
Area of Effect: Special
Saving Throw: None

This spell lets the caster store a spell in a staff, which casts the spell each time it is used to attack a creature. Immediately after casting this spell, the caster should attempt to cast a 1st-level spell that can target a point or a creature other than the caster (or one that gives the caster a weapon to make a touch attack against a creature). Instead of being cast, this spell will be stored in a Spellstaff, which is wielded by the caster.

