This spell brings forth a magical object that imbues creatures that see it with the desire to be near it. Any non-allied creature that sees the object of sympathy must make a Will save (with -3 DC) each round or be compelled to walk harmlessly toward the object for the round. Any creature immune to charm effects is also immune to this effect.~
@37760     = ~Skip Time~
@38760     = ~Skip Time
