Duration: 10 rounds
Casting Time: 2
Area of Effect: Party
Saving Throw: None

Skip Time transports the party ten rounds into the future. From the point of view of other creatures, the party vanishes, then reappears in the same spot ten rounds later. However, no time has passed for the party.

