Spell Turning reflects incoming hostile spells back at the source. While Spell Turning is active, if the caster would be hit by a harmful, single-target spell of any level, that spell is reflected back at its own caster. Spell Turning can reflect a total of 15 spell levels before it ends, though as long as there is at least one spell level remaining, the next spell will be reflected. It does not reflect Dispel Magic either, though it cannot be dispelled itself.~
@37764     = ~Steal Effects~
