Simulacrum creates a duplicate of the caster, which will serve the caster for the duration. It has half the caster's hit points and half the caster's level (rounded up) in each of the caster's classes. The simulacrum retains the memorized spells of the caster, which it can cast as well (but only those of a low enough level). It has no equipment, so it is useful primarily as an extra spellcaster. A character can only have one simulacrum at a time.~
@37863     = ~Reverse Gravity~
@38863     = ~Reverse Gravity
